        <detaileddescription>
<para>Dequeues the all blocks from a locked FIFO.</para>
<para>This is equivalent to calling <ref refid="group__fifo_1ga2734c4d814d8f2b6b2c0edbb12e1bb92" kindref="member">vlc_fifo_DequeueUnlocked()</ref> repeatedly until the FIFO is emptied, but this function is much faster.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>This function is not a cancellation point.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="warning"><para>The FIFO must be locked by the calling thread using <ref refid="group__fifo_1gae03d77fb47001cfb35223b0b3cdc28df" kindref="member">vlc_fifo_Lock()</ref>. Otherwise behaviour is undefined.</para>
</simplesect>
